{
  "id": "adv_group_thrx_02_03",
  "title": "IIIX 02 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、『ERFOLG』って数年で販売終了したわよね\nそんなに熱心だったなら、どうして辞めちゃったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But ERFOLG stopped selling after a few years‚ didn't it?\nIf you were so passionate about it‚ why did you quit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.549999809300001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ that's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "endTime": 12.2071202119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "（あ～あ、山田さんってば）\n（聞かれたくないこと聞かれちゃったって感じ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Aww‚ Yamada-san~)\n(It looks like she got asked something she didn't want to hear about.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4,
      "endTime": 19.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "（ま～、誰にだって言いたくないことくらいあるけど）\n（……kanaにだって、いくらでも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Well~‚ everyone has things they don't want to talk about.)\n(…Kana has plenty of them too.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2,
      "endTime": 28.6684350968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "（お母さんの顔は知らない）\n（kanaを産んだ時に死んじゃったらしいから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I don't know my mother's face.)\n(She apparently died when she gave birth to me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6,
      "endTime": 37.699999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "（お父さんはいるけど）\n（仕事が忙しくて、ほとんど家にはいなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I have a father‚ but)\n(he was always busy with work and barely ever home.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9,
      "endTime": 44.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、年に数回だけ帰ってきた時には）\n（kanaと一日遊んでくれたから、それで良かったの）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But when he came home a few times a year‚)\n(he would play with me all day‚ and that was enough.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4666666667,
      "endTime": 53.8172791163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "（でも「お前の父親は病気だからもう会えない」って）\n（祖父さんに言われて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But then my grandfather told me‚ \"Your father is sick and you can't see him anymore‚\" )\n(and…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5666666667,
      "endTime": 64.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "（それからお父さんは一度も帰ってこなかった）\n（kanaは、寂しいのを我慢してずっと待ってたのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(My father never came home again.)\n(I endured the loneliness and kept waiting.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9666666667,
      "endTime": 76.0999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "（爺に言われて、キッズモデルになったのはその後）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And then I became a child model‚ just like my grandfather told me to.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7,
      "endTime": 81.033288002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "（理由？　孫で小遣い稼ぎでもしたかったんじゃないの）\n（うちの爺、どこに出しても恥ずかしいクソだったし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Why? Did he just want to make some extra money off his granddaughter?)\n(My grandpa was a piece of garbage‚ an embarrassment to everyone.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8,
      "endTime": 93.9999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "（好きで始めた訳じゃないけど意外と楽しかった）\n（それに、モデルになっていいこともあったし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It wasn't like I started because I wanted to‚ but it was surprisingly fun.)\n(And there were some good things about being a model.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7,
      "endTime": 103.3172559738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "（……まだ一つ、叶ってない夢もあるけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…Though there's still one unfulfilled dream.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2333333333,
      "endTime": 109.0538320859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――VENUSグランプリ　準決勝当日、開演数時間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the Venus Grand Prix semi-finals‚ several hours before the performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4666666667,
      "endTime": 113.69999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "いい、これからご挨拶するのはイベントの主催者達よ\nくれぐれも粗相がないようにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ we're going to greet the event organizers now.\nDon't do anything stupid.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6333333333,
      "endTime": 121.73859656159999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "うっさいな、分かってるって\nkana、mihoより業界歴長いんですけど～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shut up‚ I know.\nKana's been in the industry longer than you‚ you know~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9333333333,
      "endTime": 129.246132456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "そういう態度だから不安になるんでしょ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why we're worried…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4333333333,
      "endTime": 132.8624942143,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 134.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "テレビ局幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "TV",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-tvkanbu001.m4a",
      "text": "やあ、kanaちゃん\n随分背が高くなったね、見違えたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ kana-chan.\nYou've grown so much‚ I hardly recognized you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7333333333,
      "endTime": 142.1733333979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "うわあ～～、おじさま、お久しぶりです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa~‚ it's been a while‚ mister!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3666666667,
      "endTime": 146.4535147349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "もう、いつの話してるんですか～～！\nkana、もうこんなに大きくなったんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been ages~!\nLook how much Kana's grown!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6666666667,
      "endTime": 153.3879493664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "大変ご無沙汰しております、局長\nkanaと親しくていらっしゃったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while‚ Director.\nYou seem close to kana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.9333333333,
      "endTime": 160.6162812732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "テレビ局幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "TV",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-tvkanbu002.m4a",
      "text": "franちゃんも久しぶり。kanaちゃんには、僕が\nプロデューサーの頃、子役として出てもらったからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while‚ fran-chan. kana-chan‚ well‚ she\nappeared in a show I produced when I was still a producer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.8333333333,
      "endTime": 168.06666666659999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "テレビ局幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "TV",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-tvkanbu003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、kanaちゃん、まだあのお祖父さんと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ kana-chan‚ are you still with your grandfather…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.2666666667,
      "endTime": 172.89999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_03-kan015.m4a",
